cc:Work.dc:title: Ghostbird Spaceflight logo
cc:Work.dc:description: The banner for the company Ghostbird Spaceflight. It depicts Ghostbird as Athene Noctua perched on a white circle inscribed with “Ghostbird” and “Spaceflight” in the typeface Caslon Roman. This emblem is set on a dark blue field with scattered, white, five-pointed stars.
